item.title: In Moments like these I Sing Out a Song
item.description: In moments like these I sing out a song, I sing out a love song to Jesus. In moments like these, I lift up my hands, I lift up my hands to the Lord. Singing, I love You, Lord, Singing, I love You, Lord Singing, I love You, Lord, I love You
